<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="456" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="0.[235,2111,698,1131]" box="[463,1842,798,865]" pageId="0" pageNumber="456">POSSUMS AND SCALY-TAILED POSSUM)</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[235,2111,698,1131]" pageId="0" pageNumber="456">• Smallto medium-sized arboreal marsupials; soft and woolly fur and dense underfur; often varied color patterns between sexes; round heads with short rostra, naked rhinaria, and forward-directed eyes; strongly prehensile tails.</paragraph>
<caption box="[1230,1438,1098,1131]" inLine="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="456" startId="0.[1230,1243,1098,1131]" targetBox="[1477,1792,1113,1302]" targetPageId="0">
