</caption>
<caption box="[1230,1577,1296,1329]" inLine="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="456" startId="0.[1230,1243,1296,1329]" targetBox="[215,1161,904,1528]" targetPageId="0">
<paragraph blockId="0.[1230,2110,1296,1526]" box="[1230,1577,1296,1329]" pageId="0" pageNumber="456">• Australasian Region.</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1230,2110,1296,1526]" pageId="0" pageNumber="456">• Lowland, montane, and tropical rainforests to sclerophyll forests and woodlands.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1230,2110,1296,1526]" box="[1230,1704,1414,1447]" pageId="0" pageNumber="456">• 6 genera, 29 species, 43 taxa.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1230,2110,1296,1526]" pageId="0" pageNumber="456">• 4 species Critically Endangered, 2 species Endangered, 3 species Vulnerable; none Extinct since 1600.</paragraph>
